OL,3,CFootage shows oyster reef 'size of a
OL,4,Cfootball pitch' after restoration
OL,6,FUnderwater video has been captured of
OL,7,Fan oyster reef, the size of a football
OL,8,Fpitch, following restoration efforts.
OL,10,FIt showed the habitat in the River
OL,11,FHamble, which is home to around 30,000
OL,12,Foysters, had settled, established and
OL,13,Fbegun forming a complex ecosystem, all
OL,14,Fwithin two years of being planted.
OL,16,FThe mollusc acts as a natural water
OL,17,Ffilter, cleaning up to 100 litres per
OL,18,Foyster per day.
