OL,6,FThe Solent Seascape Project teamed up
OL,7,Fwith the Royal Navy to capture what is
OL,8,Fbelieved to be the first-ever moving
OL,9,Ffootage of the ecosystem.
OL,11,FComparing the newly revived areas to
OL,12,Fthe unrestored areas, researchers say
OL,13,Fthey saw a striking contrast in
OL,14,Fhabitat quality.
OL,16,FThose working on the project say it
OL,17,Fshows the benefits of restoring and
OL,18,Fprotecting marine habitats for
OL,19,Fbiodiversity and to improve the long-
OL,20,Fterm health of coastal environments.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
