OL,4,Cfootball pitch' after restoration
OL,6,FDr Luke Helmer, who's the Restoration
OL,7,FScience Manager at Blue Marine, said:
OL,8,F"It was amazing to get eyes on the
OL,9,Freef for the first time in such detail,
OL,11,F"We are very grateful for the Royal
OL,12,FNavy's support in this endeavour. It
OL,13,Fwas a nice surprise, observing how
OL,14,Fquickly the reef community has
OL,15,Festablished and is now flourishing.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
