OL,3,CFootage shows oyster reef 'size of a
OL,4,Cfootball pitch' after restoration
OL,6,F"It was great to see so many sponges,
OL,7,Fa big spider crab and quite a few fish
OL,8,Fspecies in a relatively short
OL,9,Foperation. It really highlights the
OL,10,Fimportance of this habitat and why we
OL,11,Fneed it back."
OL,13,FThe Solent's oyster population has
OL,14,Fbeen declining over the past two
OL,15,Fdecades due to pollution, invasive
OL,16,Fspecies, disease, and over-fishing.
