OL,6,FThe restoration efforts of four
OL,7,Fhectares of the habitat started in
OL,8,F2023. The first phase involved placing
OL,9,F468 tonnes of gravel and shell over a
OL,10,Fquarter of a hectare of the riverbed.
OL,11,FAround 15,000 native oysters were then
OL,12,Fintroduced to the site.
OL,14,FIn 2025, further work was done to
OL,15,Fdouble the size of the reef and add an
OL,16,Fextra 15,000 oysters.
OL,18,FCommander Rory Armstrong, Commanding
OL,19,FOfficer DTXG added: "We take very
OL,20,Fseriously our environmental
OL,21,Fobligations.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
